change paths in *.desktop files to current directory
cp the desktop files to /usr/share/xessions (gdm or any other
standards-compliant login manager will look in this dir for xsession files)

sudo cp gs-awesome.desktop /usr/share/xsessions
sudo cp gs-gnome.desktop /usr/share/xsessions

look into .xsession-errors in case of errors

for Ubuntu 11.4 (with gnome 2.32) do the following:

sudo cp ubuntu/awesome.session /usr/share/gnome-session/sessions/awesome.session
